videos.description: Jordan Murphy penetrates and dishes to Reggie Lynch for the jam as the Gophers jump to an early lead over the Friars.
videos.headline: Murphy drives and drops to Lynch for slam

videos.description: Nate Mason wastes no time draining a three early in the shot clock as Minnesota leads Providence 12-2 early.
videos.headline: Mason launches three as Gophers get hot start

videos.description: Providence's Makai Ashton-Langford finds Nate Watson from half court and Watson slams it home as the Friars have cut the deficit to 14-12.
videos.headline: Providence pushes tempo with long pass and dunk

videos.description: Providence's Kyron Cartwright leads Alpha Diallo with a bounce pass and Diallo finishes in transition as the Friars trail the Golden Gophers by one.
videos.headline: Cartwright sets up dunk with precise bounce pass

videos.description: Providence's Isaiah Jackson spots up behind the arc and nails a three to tie Minnesota 27-27.
videos.headline: Jackson's triple ties it up

videos.description: Providence's Kyron Cartwright gets to the elbow and drains a tough jumper over the Minnesota defender.
videos.headline: Cartwright nails jumper, wants foul

videos.description: Minnesota's Isaiah Washington nails a jumper at the buzzer, but it is called off after review as the Friars hold a 39-36 lead over the Golden Gophers at the half.
videos.headline: Gophers' buzzer-beater called off

videos.description: Minnesota's Jordan Murphy drives and finishes over the Friars' defense and gets the foul call as the Gophers cut the deficit to 46-43.
videos.headline: Murphy displays strength with and-1 throw down

videos.description: Providence fends off Minnesota in the second half as Makai Ashton-Langford hesitates and rises to sink the floater to give the Friars a 53-50 lead.
videos.headline: Ashton-Langford hesitates to create space

videos.description: Minnesota swings momentum in their favor as Isaiah Washington steals the rebound and finds Dupree McBrayer who slashes to the rim for the finish.
videos.headline: Hustle play gives Gophers momentum

videos.description: Amir Coffey pump fakes to get the Friar defender off his feet and drains the three to go up nine in the second half.
videos.headline: Gophers open up lead with wide-open triple
